[
    {
        "text": "Common sense tells us that when the risks are weighed, the decisions are made very differently.",
        "startTime": 600,
        "endTime": 4930,
        "slowStartTime": 1040,
        "slowEndTime": 7450
    },
    {
        "text": "When crimes against humanity...",
        "startTime": 6470,
        "endTime": 8000,
        "slowStartTime": 9750,
        "slowEndTime": 11990
    },
    {
        "text": "...are punished consistently and severely,...",
        "startTime": 9300,
        "endTime": 12610,
        "slowStartTime": 14190,
        "slowEndTime": 18960
    },
    {
        "text": "...the killer's calculus will change,...",
        "startTime": 12950,
        "endTime": 14780,
        "slowStartTime": 19580,
        "slowEndTime": 22200
    },
    {
        "text": "...and when a killer is allowed to walk away from his crimes,...",
        "startTime": 15780,
        "endTime": 19200,
        "slowStartTime": 23780,
        "slowEndTime": 28830
    },
    {
        "text": "...I believe that also tells him something.",
        "startTime": 19950,
        "endTime": 21880,
        "slowStartTime": 30005,
        "slowEndTime": 32800
    },
    {
        "text": "It sends a message to the next that they need not worry,...",
        "startTime": 22450,
        "endTime": 24890,
        "slowStartTime": 33795,
        "slowEndTime": 37500
    },
    {
        "text": "...that they will most likely not be held accountable for their actions.",
        "startTime": 25990,
        "endTime": 29490,
        "slowStartTime": 39145,
        "slowEndTime": 44255
    },
    {
        "text": "I believe that the existence of trials alone has the potential to change behavior,...",
        "startTime": 31770,
        "endTime": 35700,
        "slowStartTime": 47845,
        "slowEndTime": 53625
    },
    {
        "text": "...but ultimately, we need to arrest those who are indicted.",
        "startTime": 37100,
        "endTime": 40240,
        "slowStartTime": 55815,
        "slowEndTime": 60310
    },
    {
        "text": "And the Sudanese arrest of Ali Kushayb appears to be a positive development,...",
        "startTime": 42180,
        "endTime": 45720,
        "slowStartTime": 63355,
        "slowEndTime": 68660
    },
    {
        "text": "...but not if it becomes a bargaining chip...",
        "startTime": 46940,
        "endTime": 49010,
        "slowStartTime": 70460,
        "slowEndTime": 73620
    },
    {
        "text": "...that will stop others from being brought to justice.",
        "startTime": 49750,
        "endTime": 51890,
        "slowStartTime": 74705,
        "slowEndTime": 77905
    },
    {
        "text": "Without an arrest, we tell the victims of these atrocities that impunity is the rule of law.",
        "startTime": 56150,
        "endTime": 60690,
        "slowStartTime": 84330,
        "slowEndTime": 91105
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I don't know if the ICC is the answer,...",
        "startTime": 63420,
        "endTime": 66130,
        "slowStartTime": 95240,
        "slowEndTime": 99255
    },
    {
        "text": "...and I don't know what type of court is...",
        "startTime": 67300,
        "endTime": 69270,
        "slowStartTime": 101055,
        "slowEndTime": 104065
    },
    {
        "text": "...or what it would need to be for all of us to agree and make it strong enough.",
        "startTime": 69400,
        "endTime": 73080,
        "slowStartTime": 104205,
        "slowEndTime": 109695
    },
    {
        "text": "I have no idea.",
        "startTime": 74000,
        "endTime": 75070,
        "slowStartTime": 111055,
        "slowEndTime": 112640
    },
    {
        "text": "And after seven years of traveling into the field, I find that I have a lot I need to learn.",
        "startTime": 76810,
        "endTime": 81340,
        "slowStartTime": 115285,
        "slowEndTime": 122035
    },
    {
        "text": "But I do know this,...",
        "startTime": 83210,
        "endTime": 84310,
        "slowStartTime": 124900,
        "slowEndTime": 126475
    },
    {
        "text": "...no mother who had her children killed in front of her,...",
        "startTime": 85450,
        "endTime": 88060,
        "slowStartTime": 128305,
        "slowEndTime": 132150
    },
    {
        "text": "...no young girl sold into slavery,...",
        "startTime": 88850,
        "endTime": 90790,
        "slowStartTime": 133385,
        "slowEndTime": 136270
    },
    {
        "text": "...no boy kidnapped and forced to be a child soldier,...",
        "startTime": 91860,
        "endTime": 94790,
        "slowStartTime": 137885,
        "slowEndTime": 142225
    },
    {
        "text": "...and no young girl like the three-year-old I met in Sierra Leone who had her limbs cut off...",
        "startTime": 96030,
        "endTime": 100230,
        "slowStartTime": 144080,
        "slowEndTime": 150435
    },
    {
        "text": "...should be expected to simply forget.",
        "startTime": 100800,
        "endTime": 103000,
        "slowStartTime": 151295,
        "slowEndTime": 154520
    },
    {
        "text": "No one should have to choose between peace or justice,...",
        "startTime": 103830,
        "endTime": 107440,
        "slowStartTime": 155800,
        "slowEndTime": 161235
    },
    {
        "text": "...and that young boy in Darfur who asked for a trial deserves one.",
        "startTime": 108000,
        "endTime": 112170,
        "slowStartTime": 162135,
        "slowEndTime": 168270
    }
]